data.description: Seller will provide $10,000 toward buyers closing costs or interest rate reduction. Ideal Blend of Comfort and Convenience: Spacious Home in a Prime Location! Explore the perfect balance of comfort and practicality in this impeccably maintained residence. The thoughtfully designed floor plan presents two primary suites and a main-level office with a built-in desk, catering to your work-from-home requirements. The kitchen, complete with a gas stove and a convenient walk-in pantry, provides all the essentials for effortless meal preparation. Step outside to enjoy the deck and yard, offering a lovely space for pets and gatherings with loved ones. Storage needs are met with the generously sized tandem garage. Situated within walking distance of the MAX line, shopping centers, and restaurants, this property offers the ultimate convenience in a tidy and inviting home. Don?t miss out on this outstanding opportunity!
